            "text_yAeUkg": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "custom_css": "",
                "text": "<p>The ultimate podcast for dance fans who crave the inside scoop. Hosted by Abby Lee Miller, the podcast dives deep into the world of competitive dance, serving up all the behind-the-scenes drama, studio rivalries, and reality show revelations fans love. <br/><br/>Each episode offers a mix of juicy gossip, expert commentary, and exclusive interviews with dancers, choreographers, and industry pros. Whether it's breaking news or untold stories, Leave It on the Dance Floor doesn't hold back—this is where the real drama unfolds.</p>",
                "width": "100%",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "rte",
